This is a demo module built as an exercise. It creates a new Promo entity type
that's primary purpose is to store a URL and an image file. The module provides
a function to fetch a single promo at random and render it as an HTML <img> tag
wrapped in an <a> tag.

Useful functions provided by this module:

- promo_get_promo_markup()
-- Returns the markup (image tag wrapped in link tag) of a random promo.
-- Usage: $markup = promo_get_promo_markup();
          print($markup)


